name: Virtual Pet Simulator (VPS) in Java.
tagline: Simple GUI Pet Simulation in Java
body:
# VirtualPetSimulator (VPS)
Pet Simulation in Java created by @Metatricity. See the current version on GitHub or read the README for more information.

***

## Versions
* Alpha 1.1 (stable)
* Alpha 1.2 
* Alpha 1.3 (unstable)
* Alpha 1.4 (stable)
* Alpha 1.5 (current, stable)

***

## Version flags
* Stable - Good for use, should be used.
* Unstable - Should not be used and should only be debugged.
* Current - The latest version of VPS.

***

## Expected Date of 1.6 alpha release.
* 3/26/2016
